115
00:09:40,704 --> 00:09:41,728
I've heard that

116
00:09:41,728 --> 00:09:44,799
not only was his portrait made into
a life-size doll,

117
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:47,320
but also a jade statue was carved for him.

118
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,559
Miss! Miss!

119
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:55,799
Outside… Outside…

120
00:10:05,491 --> 00:10:06,200
