122
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:09,879
Looks exactly like the character
from Lady Wen's storybook.

123
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:11,639
This is Xiao Chen, the Seventh Prince.

124
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:13,600
There really is a Seventh Prince?!

125
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,840
Miss, you're so incredible.

126
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,519
The Seventh Prince is really named Xiao Chen.

127
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:19,039
And he is exactly the same as
described in your storybook.

128
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:20,360
He is also a member of the Imperial Guard.

129
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,279
It is said
that he is the Emperor's illegitimate son.

130
00:10:22,279 --> 00:10:24,200
He was taken out of the imperial palace
shortly after birth.

131
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:28,200
He was only summoned back to the capital
after what happened to the Crown Prince.

132
00:10:33,519 --> 00:10:38,360
Miss, he looks exactly like the portrait
you painted.

